title: Michelle Obama feels the burn at SoulCycle in DC | Daily Mail Online
text: EXCLUSIVE: Michelle Obama feels the burn at SoulCycle in Washington DC after family returns home via private jet from long weekend ski trip to Aspen Michelle Obama was photographed leaving a SoulCycle class in Washington DC on Thursday afternoon This is the first time Michelle has been spotted in Washington DC since leaving the capital after President Trump's inauguration Michelle, 53, took a class at noon and then quickly made her way back to her Secret Service detail after the session was over She managed to keep her identity a secret from most around her by covering her face with large sunglasses and a dark hat Her outing on Thursday came the day after members of the family returned home from an Aspen ski vacation on a private jet belonging to friends Up in the Big Apple, Malia grabbed a cab into work at The Weinsten Group just a few days ahead of the Oscars, where their film Lion has six nominations Published: 21:03 GMT, 23 February 2017 | Updated: 22:09 GMT, 23 February 2017 44 shares
